replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:33:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0377b6dac9b9ded7ba8a54f3845289d088f94b7a","tid":1922031,"uid":235693,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:33:39.000Z","msg":"賣成180蚊，國家冇錢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3cfdc59239aa09dd2c292f09b480318ae0f737","tid":1922031,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"仲以為送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579a2244a22f7ead7d09425df49723924585cff0","tid":1922031,"uid":75519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ad606c0f2187be1c5948a416d6e5db82f73d9b1","tid":1922031,"uid":274390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"係時候係全球發起Asian Not Chinese 行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1922003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1922003</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a186f4f77894a0e63370fa4b3342c10f9911f83a","tid":1922031,"uid":36245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>大文集團出版 《哭泣的城市》畫冊3．23開售</strong><br />\n時間：2020-03-12 04:23:18來源：大公報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMTtyOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMTtyOY.jpg&h=a4a07014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　圖：圖片節錄自《哭泣的城市》畫冊，畫冊從3月23日起將在全港書店發售<br />\n　　【大公報訊】大公文匯傳媒集團昨日公布，即將出版《哭泣的城市──香港修例風波實錄》大型畫冊，輯錄大文記者在一線拍攝的大量珍貴圖片，並配以圖表和文章，旨在還原真相，激濁揚清，警醒世人，讓正義之聲成為社會的最強音。市民對畫冊即將發售的消息反應熱烈，紛紛致電詢問，期待早日出版。<br />\n　　《哭泣的城市──香港修例風波實錄》畫冊以大量新聞圖片、評論文章、圖表、漫畫以及視頻新聞（二維碼），忠實地記錄了修例風波爆發以來的事態發展，以全方位的視角真實記錄這場風波的全貌。<br />\n　　2019年6月起，一場大規模黑色暴亂，來得如此突然，如此驚心動魄，直至暴亂大半年後的今天，很多人仍無法理解：文明法治的香港為何一夜間淪為妖獸世界？<br />\n　　真實記錄，是對歷史的銘記。守護香港，就是守護我們共同的未來。<br />\n　　《哭泣的城市》編委會表示，有關市場銷售工作正在全力進行，3月23日起，香港三聯書店、商務印書館、中華書局、<a href=\"http://網上書店超閱網SuperBookcity.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E8%B6%85%E9%96%B1%E7%B6%B2SuperBookcity.com&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=a8e204a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">網上書店超閱網SuperBookcity.com</a>將全線上架銷售畫冊精裝版。有興趣的讀者可先向書店預訂。"},{"pid":"dc6f2555ee8cb96628ee59b79cc1a34e36eacb45","tid":1922031,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee60e8d29c137e53f9253276da32248cfff4871","tid":1922031,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:06:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c58d02c3a26e43836d3c076e70b0ba825987e673","tid":1922031,"uid":249160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要賣$180<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍屍窮撚會買咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6f02d0095eecec02f0ea66da5fffb9b0a12435","tid":1922031,"uid":158888,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"蘋果嗰本一出就斷貨<br />\n睇吓呢本A貨過幾日仲有冇得賣"},{"pid":"1842dbfac4144b25562e054a